{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The initial plan had been to send-- to pick up basically 1,000 of these stray kids, and bring them to the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were successful in getting 200 over here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were basically two transports.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There may have been a third one later on that I'm reading about now, but I'm not 100% sure of this one.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "From what I've read, the way they tried to pick the children, they tried to pick the kids who would have the least chance of survival in France-- which means the foreign-born kids, not the French kids.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If you had relatives in France, the chances are you could not go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If your parents have been deported, the chances are that you would be put on the list.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was picked, along with all the other kids in my particular room at Montintin, to be on the first transport of 100 children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "For some reason or other, the transport left in about May-- about May of 1941.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The children were assembled, not only from Chateau Montintin, but also from some of the other homes, like Masgelier, and-- let's see, there was Masgelier, there was Chateau Chabanne-- there were several other homes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were all sent to Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And from there on in, the Quakers did a lot of paperwork and processing the paperwork, so, to get the-- to get the kids out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And 100 children, then, arrived in the United States June 22nd, 1941.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that was the first transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now, I was supposed to go on the first transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I had been picked for it, myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And, for some reason or other, approximately a week before the transport was supposed to leave, I was told I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I've been taken off the transport-- myself and another girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
